title: Jabberwocky
creator: Lewis Carroll
description: LibriVox volunteers bring you 34 different recordings of Jabberwocky, by Lewis Carroll. This was the weekly poetry project for the week of January 21st, 2007. For more information on our readers, please visit the catalog page at: http://librivox.org/jabberwocky-by-lewis-carroll/. For more free audiobooks, or to become a volunteer reader, please visit librivox.org. Download M4B (26MB)
